title: College freshmen are stressed and cannot adjust emotionally to campus life, survey says
text:
College freshmen are stressed and cannot adjust emotionally to campus life, survey says 
Published By: Cleveland.com - Today 
Many college freshmen are prepared academically but not emotionally for campus life, according to a new national survey....
